  "general_provisions": "This bill modifies provisions relating to educator license discipline and restrictions on employment and volunteer service.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>amends provisions relating to ineligibility for educator licensure following license denial;<hr><ltbullet>establishes a tiered framework for restrictions on employment and volunteer service following license suspension or revocation;<hr><ltbullet>requires automatic restrictions for serious misconduct involving actual harm or credible risk to children;<hr><ltbullet>requires written findings demonstrating specific risk for restrictions in other cases;<hr><ltbullet>exempts technical violations from automatic work and volunteer restrictions;<hr><ltbullet>enacts provisions governing restrictions on employment and volunteer service following disciplinary action;<hr><ltbullet>modifies notice requirements for disciplinary proceedings; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
